# purpose

- this is a pytest plugin that runs test written in JSON

# components

- `pytest-http` is the main module of this project
- `pytest_http/pytest_plugin.py` contains pytest related code (test collection, validation and running)
- `pytest_http/models.py` contains Pydantic models for JSON tests validation
- `tests` is the testing module for this project
- `tests/**/test_*.py` files contain regular Python unit tests for the project itself
- `tests/**/test_*.http.json` files contain JSON test samples
